translate chinese dana3_5cfb9131:

    # "It's a fairly normal day of work. I work in Mrs. Mills office all day."
    "这算是个相当平常的工作日。我一整天都在米尔斯夫人的办公室里。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:11
translate chinese dana3_85a4b54e:

    # "Cleaning all the normal things."
    "打扫那些例行公事。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:13
translate chinese dana3_377c9b7e:

    # "Typing all the normal stuff."
    "录入那些例行公文。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:16
translate chinese dana3_a53d8e78:

    # "Then Mrs. Mills stops me from moving on to the next task."
    "这时，米尔斯夫人叫住了我，不让我继续做下一项任务。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:17
translate chinese dana3_c0382d9a:

    # bs "[pcname], I need you to stop what you're working on and run down to the file room."
    bs "[pcname], 我要你停下手头的工作，赶紧去档案室。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:18
translate chinese dana3_d80878d0:

    # bs "There's a list of names on my desk. I need you to pull all those files. Got it?"
    bs "我桌上有张名单。我要你把上面所有人的档案都调出来。明白了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:19
translate chinese dana3_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "是的，女士。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:22
translate chinese dana3_c7520cb7:

    # "I take the list off her desk and leave the office, walking down the hall towards the file room."
    "我从她桌上拿过名单，走出办公室，沿着走廊走向档案室。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:23
translate chinese dana3_0960d991:

    # "When I open the door, I am shocked at what I see."
    "推开门的一瞬间，眼前的景象让我大吃一惊。"

