    "她的脸涨得通红，仿佛快要高潮了。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:30
translate chinese dana3_b2e8b35d:

    # "I just stand there, in awe at what I am seeing."
    "我呆立原地，对眼前这一幕感到震惊。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:31
