    voice dana_ohmygodsosorry
    cw ""

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:38
translate chinese dana3_7e6225e6:

    # "She quickly pulls her hand out of her skirt and lets it fall back into place."
    "她迅速将手从裙子里抽出来，让裙摆重新垂落原位。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:41
translate chinese dana3_96b67724:

    # "I shut the door immediately and step back, closing my eyes, trying to push what I saw out of my mind."
    "我立刻关上门，退后几步，闭上眼睛，试图将刚才所见从脑海中驱散。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:42
translate chinese dana3_f755cfb4:

    # "Then the door flies open again."
    "接着，门又猛地豁开。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:45
translate chinese dana3_ea93a80f:

    # "She rushes out the door past me, her head turned away in shame."
    "她羞愧地扭过头，从我身旁冲了出去。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:46
translate chinese dana3_18ee2b1e:

    # cw "I'm sorry."
    cw "“对不起。”"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:47
translate chinese dana3_0a2833a9:

    # "Her face is red and there are tears in her eyes as she pushes past me and down the hall towards the lobby."
    "她脸颊通红，眼中含泪，从我身边挤过，沿着走廊奔向大堂。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:48
translate chinese dana3_52d8ece4:

    # "I think about stopping her, but I wouldn't know what to say right now, my mind is spinning in every direction."
    "我想过要拦住她，但此刻我不知该说什么，脑海里思绪纷乱。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:51
translate chinese dana3_a6923c14:

    # "Instead, I do what I have been sent to the fileroom to do and collect the files for Mrs. Mills."
    "于是，我转而去做被派往档案室的任务，为米尔斯夫人整理文件。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:52
translate chinese dana3_55bc9dc1:

    # "It only takes a few minutes, then I carry them all back to Mrs. Mills' office."
    "只花了短短几分钟，我就把所有文件都搬回了米尔斯夫人的办公室。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:55
translate chinese dana3_86da1330:

    # "I put them all down on the table and get ready to move on to my next task."
    "我把它们全都放在桌上，准备开始下一项任务。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:57
translate chinese dana3_03d82cdf:

    # "Then there's a short knock on the door and it opens. Dana stands there in the doorway."
    "这时门外传来轻轻的敲门声，门开了。达娜站在门口。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:60
translate chinese dana3_056188dd:

    # cw "Mrs. Mills, I've had an emergency come up."
    cw "“米尔斯女士，我遇到紧急情况了。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:61
translate chinese dana3_70f872b5:

    # cw "Can I please take the rest of the day off?"
    cw "今天剩下的时间能请假吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:66
translate chinese dana3_25f979f8:

    # bs "Oh no, is everything okay?"
    bs "“哦，不，一切都还好吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:67
translate chinese dana3_4176ace6:

    # cw "I'm not sure yet. I just need to go home."
    cw "“我还不确定。我只是需要回家。”"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:68
translate chinese dana3_d8473bac:

    # bs "Okay, take the rest of the day off. If you need more, give me a call tomorrow."
    bs "“好的，今天剩下的时间你请假吧。如果需要更多时间，明天给我打电话。”"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:69
translate chinese dana3_878246f2:

    # cw "Yes, ma'am, thank you."
    cw "“是的，女士，谢谢您。”"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:71
translate chinese dana3_286e8647:

    # "She quickly shuts the door and rushes away."
    "她迅速关上门，匆匆离去。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:72
translate chinese dana3_f0ea3fe4:

    # "She never even looked at me."
    "她甚至都没看我一眼。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:73
translate chinese dana3_27b21c19:

    # bs "Poor girl. I hope everything is okay."
    bs "可怜的孩子。希望一切都好。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:74
translate chinese dana3_1a28adf6:

    # "It feels like work is about to become super-awkward."
    "感觉工作氛围马上就要变得超级尴尬了。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:75
translate chinese dana3_60f1a3d3:

    # "Why was she doing that in the file room anyways?"
    "她到底为什么要在档案室做那种事呢？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:76
translate chinese dana3_79f7f898:

    # "I think about telling Mrs. Mills about it, but I decide I don't want to get her in trouble."
    "我本想告诉米尔斯夫人这件事，但转念一想，我不想让她惹上麻烦。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:77
translate chinese dana3_fcaa87ad:

    # "I spend the rest of the day working, unable to get Dana out of my head."
    "剩下的时间我都在工作，却始终无法将达娜从脑海中赶出去。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/dana3.rpy:78
translate chinese dana3_b0a0c6bf:

    # "Until finally it is time to leave for the day. Mrs. Mills and I say our goodbyes and I go out to the car."
    "直到终于到了下班的时候。 我和米尔斯夫人道别后，走向了停车场。"

